  },
  {
    q: "How do I get more Google reviews from my customers?",
    a: "The most effective method is a direct ask at the right moment. For dine-in, this is when the bill arrives. For delivery, it is 30 to 40 minutes after delivery via a WhatsApp follow-up. We set up automated WhatsApp messages and provide table cards or QR codes that make it a one-tap action for customers. The key is making the process effortless. Restaurants that actively ask for reviews consistently collect 5 to 10 times more than those who do not."
  },
